Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:23.66,Screen_Place,,780,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)\an2\blur2\shad3\fs70}麗麗亞
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.61,Screen_Place,,580,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an2\be1\bord1\fs70}卡爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.61,Screen_Place,,580,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an2\blur2\shad3\fs70}卡爾
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.04,Screen_Place,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an2\be1\bord1\fs70}尼魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.04,Screen_Place,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an2\blur2\shad3\fs70}尼魯
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.72,Screen_Place,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an2\be1\bord1\fs70}伊茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.72,Screen_Place,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an2\blur2\shad3\fs70}伊茲
